s82: Fourteenth year: Yue besieged Wu; Wu resented this.
s277: Wei Huan Zi defeated Zhi Bo at Jin Yang.
s279: Fifth year: Xiang Zi defeated Zhi Bo at Jin Yang, and together with Wei and Han divided his territory into three parts.
s285: Twenty-fifth year: Jin grandee Zhi Kai led his city in coming to submit.
